User
    ident     Text
    password  Text Maybe
    UniqueUser ident
  deriving Show

Project
    name      Text
    created   Day
  deriving Show

Todo
    title     Text
    done      Bool
    asap      Bool
    date      Day
    created   Day
    memo      Text
    user      UserId
    project   ProjectId
  deriving Show

TagTodo
    tag       TagId
    todo      TodoId
    UniqueTagTodo
  deriving Show

Tag
    name      Text
  deriving Show

Email
    email Text
    user UserId Maybe
    verkey Text Maybe
    UniqueEmail email
  deriving Show

 -- By default this file is used in Model.hs (which is imported by Foundation.hs)
